{"tid":797933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停職警涉於福華街偷32大元物品被捕 今日提堂","createTime":"2018-08-29T02:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T03:15:40.000Z","uid":136994,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e561c74537a53eb1d3a4438c1d7ff648c1224cf9","tid":797933,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/bkn-20180829002029579-0829_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180829%2Fbkn-20180829002029579-0829_00822_001.html&d=%2F7PvxGVesDDcZSZb%2Fw0AhQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=cc6f5b17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/bkn-20180829002029579-0829_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/photo/bkn-20180829002029579-0829_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180829082627\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180829002029579-0829_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180829082627&h=02db74f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n停職警長涉盜竊被控！一名姓張(51歲)原本駐守九龍城分區的軍裝警長，因涉及一宗案件，多年前已被停職。今年5月18日下午4時許，他在深水埗福華街一間用品特價店內，被發現疑偷走手電筒、拉鏈袋、行李牌及眼鏡夾等4件貨品，總值32港元，職員報警將他拘捕。警方經調查後，他已被控以一項盜竊罪，今日(29日)在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍及姑息，必定嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警察個個都係好人<br />\n32蚊嘢都要偷</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae385cd3b9929f4b9ef0f6aaea93946df87db435","tid":797933,"uid":23734,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"一日最衰都係佔中,搞到嗰個警員壓力咁大,要偷$32既野"},{"pid":"9f02c5f447151a479a475f1b69cf67f35d5ea00c","tid":797933,"uid":116054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"32蚊！真係好窮咩？定係慣左又食又拎！"},{"pid":"14e021c3ca7cc4653b1b706485d2133c9dc65e4d","tid":797933,"uid":46595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:30:52.000Z","msg":"騖人做野唔洗你教!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8177ca5d93a7ca9c3ea38b2809f3face278b100","tid":797933,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:30:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警方重申，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍及姑息，必定嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"637239263ba176184da0429f20987e824beabd11","tid":797933,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"5月犯案, 今日先提堂<br />\n盜竊唔係多數好快架咩<br />\n又唔使查"},{"pid":"ea13f3a83b6ccdcf51ae66ae17ad446528165fc1","tid":797933,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:34:41.000Z","msg":"係咪上次係ssp特賣城偷耳筒果條天才"},{"pid":"48241897a0d19740617b5cc0a92fe2bb9fd7a2b6","tid":797933,"uid":69910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae385cd3b9929f4b9ef0f6aaea93946df87db435","tid":797933,"uid":23734,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"一日最衰都係佔中,搞到嗰個警員壓力咁大,要偷$32既野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"agger 一定關佔中事"},{"pid":"fae45d2a0f2066c0c2bcb1a4b17a53cc7984d480","tid":797933,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:35:19.000Z","msg":"福仁嗰間嘢既嘢都偷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cb28daa1956b06bc23e4661bb9d695405c6adf","tid":797933,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:36:10.000Z","msg":"呢檔野咁開方式，年中比人偷唔小野"},{"pid":"6db77079138a2cb41041715b3775b876de1420d2","tid":797933,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48241897a0d19740617b5cc0a92fe2bb9fd7a2b6","tid":797933,"uid":69910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae385cd3b9929f4b9ef0f6aae